Performance improvements.
Fixes.

- FLIGHT SIMULATOR with WORLDWIDE TERRAIN and NAVIGATION SYSTEM
- Radar with runway and aircraft carrier orientation
- Realistic fuel consumption
- More realistic aircraft and extreme conditions with wind, rain, snow and lightning
- 3D virtual cockpit with integrated instrumentation, rain/snow effects and 6 different camera angles visual perspectives

New Aircraft:
- F-16 Fighting Falcon
- A-7 Corsair II
- F-22 Raptor
- SU-47 Berkut
- C-130 Hercules
- EF Typhoon
